://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/383270/extras/Skulls.jpg?t=1747737955[/img]","strSnippet":"Hue is a vibrant, award-winning puzzle-adventure, where you alter the world by changing its background colour."}}]]